{"tid":1039474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞：4天326委內瑞拉軍人叛逃","createTime":"2019-02-27T12:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T15:42:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"969044a6ad10d405bb4dc387ccdbcb91063d2b70","tid":1039474,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞：4天326委內瑞拉軍人叛逃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%93%A5%E5%80%AB%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E-4%E5%A4%A9326%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%9B%E9%80%83-232203005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2593%25A5%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BA%259E-4%25E5%25A4%25A9326%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%259B%25E9%2580%2583-232203005.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4e9900b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%93%A5%E5%80%AB%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E-4%E5%A4%A9326%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%9B%E9%80%83-232203005.html</a><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞移民局26日表示，自23日以來，已經有326名委內瑞拉軍人背棄總統馬杜洛(Nicolas Maduro)，並越界進入哥倫比亞。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞移民局指出，由於主要邊界通道都已經被委內瑞拉軍隊封鎖，因此這些叛逃的委國軍人大部份是從同一個地區潛入哥倫比亞。<br />\n<br />\n哥國移民官員克魯格(Christian Kruger)表示，這些軍人是逃離馬杜洛政府的民兵組織「集體黨」(colectivos)的「獨裁」和「壓迫」。<br />\n<br />\n克魯格說，部份軍人是戴著武裝、穿著制服進入哥國，有些則是穿著便服或與家人同行。<br />\n<br />\n克魯格並未透露叛逃軍人的階級，但據信都不是高階軍官。<br />\n<br />\n克魯格說，當局將會評估這些人的背景，如果不具威脅性，將會獲准留下。<br />\n<br />\n已被50國承認為臨時總統的委內瑞拉反對派領袖瓜伊多(Juan Guaido)曾表示，未來將會特赦背棄馬杜洛的軍人。<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多要推翻馬杜洛並舉行新的總統大選，首先必須獲得軍方高層的支持。但截至目前，軍方將領仍效忠馬杜洛。"},{"pid":"5ca7da6149e4d9ffd59012bfa68abfa0a3286a22","tid":1039474,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00006c3019b661fb95964a8630e96287de791a35","tid":1039474,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3fb31df9b33c53ed68d4f9f60faea656dc3e1e","tid":1039474,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"北韓都未革命，馬杜羅真係唔使驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd9c2d6111641689aeec365015349bd5667a7b9","tid":1039474,"uid":52946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bf3fb31df9b33c53ed68d4f9f60faea656dc3e1e","tid":1039474,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"北韓都未革命，馬杜羅真係唔使驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"北韓依家有飯吃 委內瑞拉直頭係唔接受國外物資食都無得食 點同"},{"pid":"0643ef3837e8f38de90e3a2eab95780e9b79ec40","tid":1039474,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd9c2d6111641689aeec365015349bd5667a7b9","tid":1039474,"uid":52946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bf3fb31df9b33c53ed68d4f9f60faea656dc3e1e","tid":1039474,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"北韓都未革命，馬杜羅真係唔使驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"北韓依家有飯吃 委內瑞拉直頭係唔接受國外物資食都無得食 點同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:42:35.000Z","msg":"北韓之前大飢荒都無事，委內瑞拉仲可以做難民走去哥倫比亞，唔使革命搵命博。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}